        <Parent_String>Central Democratic Republic of Congo styles [300016309], Central African (cultural or regional style) [300016168], African by cultural or regional designation [300121001], African (general, continental cultures) [300015647], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
